    "title": "Urban Heat Island Intensity (JJA)",
    "description": "This openEO User Defined Process (UDP) computes Urban Heat Island (UHI) intensity during the summer months (June–August). It processes satellite-derived Land Surface Temperature data and compares urban pixels with surrounding rural reference areas using a configurable kernel size.",
